# Step 2: Frontend Development

## Description
Build a simple POS UI using ASP.NET Core or React.

---

## ASP.NET Core Setup

### 1. Install .NET SDK and Visual Studio
- Download and install the latest .NET SDK from https://dotnet.microsoft.com/download
- Install Visual Studio with the ASP.NET and web development workload

### 2. Create a New ASP.NET Core Web App
```bash
dotnet new webapp -n CloudPOSFrontend
cd CloudPOSFrontend

3. Design a Basic POS Interface

Use Razor Pages to create:

    A product list page
    A shopping cart page
    A checkout form

Example Razor Page for Product Listing (Pages/Products.cshtml):



